    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the courgette and tomatoes have had 5 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the<strong> crumbed chicken</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 20 min further or until the breadcrumbs are crisp and golden and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Provençal-style crumbed chicken </strong>and <strong>roasted vegetables</strong></p>",
